snippet.description:
► Website: http://www.rammstein.com
► Shop: http://shop.rammstein.de

Premiere: September 16th,  2005
Shoot: Mid August 2005, 3 days
Location: Berlin
Director: Uwe Flade
Single: Benzin
From the album: Rosenrot

The video for BENZIN, the first single of the album ROSENROT, was directed by Uwe Flade (Depeche Mode, Franz Ferdinand) and was shot in Berlin.
snippet.title: Rammstein - Benzin (Official Video)
